0from%20behind%20and%20kissed%20me%20without%20my%20consent.%20I%20was%20shocked%20and%20I%20ran%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20actor%20offered%20her%20more%20work%20if%20she%20was%20willing%20to%20be%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%2C%20the%20actor%20had%20approached%20Association%20of%20Malayalam%20Movie%20Artists%20(AMMA)%20secretary%20Idavela%20Babu%20for%20a%20membership%20application.%20She%20said%20he%20called%20her%20over%20to%20his%20flat%20on%20the%20pretense%20of%20applying%20for%20a%20membership%20of%20the%20film%20association%20and%20physically%20abused%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Muneer%20also%20said%20actor%20Mukesh%2C%C2%A0a%20MLA%20of%20the%20ruling%20CPI(M)%2C%20has%20denied%20her%20the%20membership%20after%20she%20turned%20down%20his%20advances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20exploitation%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%20I%20am%20a%20witness%20and%20victim.%20When%20I%20moved%20to%20Chennai%2C%20nobody%20reached%20out%20to%20me%2C%20asking%20me%20what%20had%20happened%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202013%2C%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20physical%20and%20verbal%20abuse%20by%20these%20individuals%20while%20working%20on%20a%20project.%20I%20tried%20to%20cooperate%20and%20continue%20working%2C%20but%20the%20abuse%20became%20unbearable.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20and%20relocate%20to%20Chennai.%20I%20had%20spoken%20out%20against%20the%20abuse%20in%20a%20newspaper%20article.%20I%20am%20now%20seeking%20justice%20and%20accountability%20for%20the%20trauma%20and%20suffering%20I%20endured.%20I%20request%20your%20assistance%20in%20taking%20action%20against%20them%20for%20their%20heinous%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20post%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20was%20accused%20of%20not%20making%20%26quot%3Badjustments%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20spoke%20up%20about%20the%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Maniyanpilla%20Raju%2C%20who%20is%20one%20of%20the%20actors%20accused%20by%20Ms%20Muneer%2C%20has%20called%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations%2C%20claiming%20multiple%20vested%20interests%20are%20behind%20the%20accusations.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20will%20try%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20situation.%20Among%20those%20accused%2C%20there%20will%20be%20both%20innocent%20and%20guilty%20parties.%20Therefore%2C%20a%20comprehensive%20investigation%20is%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20mounting%20pressure%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20held%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20with%20senior%20police%20officials%20on%20Sunday%20and%20has%20announced%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20seven-member%20special%20team%20to%20investigate%20the%20atrocities%20faced%20by%20women%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20actor%20Soniya%20Malhar%20said%20the%20victims%20have%20repeatedly%20shared%20their%20ordeal%20with%20the%20investigating%20agencies.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20need%20action%20immediately%20from%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20explain%20what%20happened%20over%20and%20over%20again.%20New%20committees%20are%20being%20formed%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20by%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%20post%20the%202017%20actress%20assault%20case%2C%20has%20revealed%20instances%20of%20harassment%20and%20exploitation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20cinema%20industry%2C%20prompting%20calls%20for%20action%20against%20the%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724659740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj9a3pnbg_minu-muneer_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmalayalam-film-actor-minu-muneer-accuses-4-co-stars-of-sexual-harassm