0href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fuddhav-thackeray%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUddhav%20Thackeray%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Sena%20wants%2016-20%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20at%20least%2015.%20The%20third%20MVA%20member%20-%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20-%20is%20believed%20to%20want%20seven%20to%20eight%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reported%20minimum%20ask%20from%20each%20party%20puts%20them%20two%20seats%20over%20that%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20the%20Sena's%20bastion%3B%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20election%20party%20(then%20undivided%20and%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP)%20won%2014%20seats%20and%20together%20the%20two%20swept%20the%20city%2C%20winning%2030%20of%2036%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20picked%20up%20four%20and%20one%2C%20respectively.%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%2C%20Aslam%20Sheikh%2C%20Amin%20Patel%2C%20and%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20were%20winners%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20Nawab%20Malik%20claimed%20the%20NCP's%20sole%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENormally%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20too%20much%20of%20a%20strain%20for%20the%20Sena%20to%20have%20its%20way%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Congress'%20showing%20in%20the%20April-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20(Ms%20Gaikwad%20won%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20seat)%2C%20gives%20the%20national%20party%20room%20to%20push%20for%20a%20greater%20share%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-uddhav-thackeray-congress-meet-discussion-on-seat-sharing-candidates-6287422%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAt%20Thackeray-Congress%20Meet%2C%20Talks%20On%20Seat%20Sharing%2C%20Candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20talks%20over%20seat-sharing%2C%20for%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state%2C%20will%20include%20discussions%20on%20'winnability'%2C%20i.e.%2C%20including%20establishing%20the%20political%20and%20demographic%20intricacies%20of%20each%20seat%20and%20which%20of%20the%20three%20parties'%20candidates%20has%20the%20best%20chance%20of%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Will%20Be%20MVA's%20Chief%20Minister%20Face%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20there%20are%20also%20disagreements%20within%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20over%20the%20alliance's%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20are%20reluctant%20to%20make%20such%20a%20declaration%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20while%20the%20Sena%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20consensus%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20option%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20-%20whose%20first%20term%20was%20cut%20short%20by%20the%20Sena-NCP%20rebellion%20-%20but%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20said%20he%20will%20back%20any%20candidate%2C%20announced%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20(SP)%2C%20as%20the%20MVA's%20candidate%20for%20the%20top%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-maharashtra-polls-uddhav-thackerays-huddle-with-congress-6277803%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWill%20Back%20Any%20MVA%20Candidate%20For%20Chief%20Minister%3A%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20the%20feeling%20I%20am%20fighting%20for%20myself%20but%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20Mumbai.%20He%20insisted%20then%20it%20would%20be%20prudent%20for%20the%20MVA%20to%20decide%20an%20alliance%20leader%20before%20the%20election%20rather%20than%20do%20so%20after%20the%20result%20-%20which%20has%20been%20the%20Congress'%20strategy%20in%20recent%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray's%20apparent%20insistence%20on%20the%20MVA%20identifying%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20a%20figure%20around%20whom%20they%20can%20build%20a%20campaign%2C%20comes%20amid%20attacks%20by%20the%20BJP%20-%20who%20will%20likely%20rely%20on%20the%20tried-and-tested%20charisma%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20win%20another%20election%20-%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20will%20likely%20also%20remember%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%202019%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sena%20and%20BJP%20won%20comfortably%20but%20the%20two%20split%20after%20failing%20to%20agree%20a%20post-poll%20chief%20ministerial%20nominee%2C%20which%20even%20included%20talk%20of%20rotating%20the%20post%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%20Miffed%20at%20being%20denied%20the%20top%20job%2C%20either%20solo%20or%20shared%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20broke%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20joined%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20On%20The%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20friction%20in%20MVA%20seat-sharing%20talks%20has%20prompted%20jibes%20from%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20with%20the%20BJP's%20Mumbai%20unit%20boss%2C%20Ashish%20Shelar%20predicting%20its%20break-up%20from%20the%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20likely%2C%20MVA%20will%20break%20over%20seat%20sharing.%20And%20if%2C%20somehow%20they%20sustain%20through%20seat%20sharing%2C%20it%20will%20break%20afterwards%20as%20three%20parties%20are%20there%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP's%20alliance%20isn't%20free%20of%20seat-sharing%20squabbles%20either%2C%20with%20the%20Sena%20group%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20the%20NCP%20faction%20of%20his%20deputy%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20pushing%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-born-in-family-of-millionaires-bjps-swipe-at-uddhav-thackeray-6322704%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThose%20Born%20In%20Family%20Of%20Millionaires...%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP's%20Swipe%20At%20Uddhav%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20poor%20showing%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20in%20which%20it%20won%20only%20nine%20of%2028%20seats%20contested%20-%20has%20given%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20more%20bargaining%20power.%20The%20Shinde%20Sena%20won%20seven%20of%2015%20seats%20contested%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20significantly%20greater%20strike-rate.%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20won%20one%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDates%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20election%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20announced.%20The%202019%20election%20was%20held%20on%20October%2021%2C%20with%20the%20Sena-BJP%20combine%20winning%20161%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA's%2098.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-mlc-election-bjp-allies-win-6-seats-pankaja-munde-wins-congress-gets-just-one-6091812%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP's%20alliance%20bounced%20back%20from%20the%20poor%20Lok%20Sabha%20showing%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20registering%20a%20big%20win%20in%20MLC%20polls.%C2%A0The%20BJP%20fielded%20five%20candidates%2C%20including%20Pankaja%20Munde%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20late%20senior%20leader%20Gopinath%20Munde.%20All%20five%20won.%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20named%20two%20each%20and%20all%20four%20won.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724658900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvjlo860g_uddhav-thackeray_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F