na%2C%20and%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Nirmal%20Singh%20and%20Kavinder%20Gupta.%20The%20list%20had%20the%20name%20of%C2%A0Union%20minister%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh's%20brother%20Devendra%20Rana%2C%20who%20switched%20from%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%2014%20Muslim%20candidates%20were%20also%20named%20in%20the%20first%20list.%C2%A0Several%20former%20leaders%20of%20Congress%2C%20National%20Conference%2C%20PDP%20and%20Panthers%20Party%2C%20who%20switched%20sides%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20now-deleted%20list.%20Some%20key%20omissions%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20led%20to%20an%20eruption%20of%20resentment%20after%20the%20first%20list%20was%20released.%20It%20is%20this%20pushback%20that%20appears%20to%20have%20forced%20the%20party%20to%20withdraw%20the%20three-phase%20list%20and%20re-release%20only%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20first%20phase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20vote%20in%20three%20phases%20on%20September%2019%2C%2025%20and%20October%201.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20October%204.%C2%A0This%20is%20the%20first%20Assembly%20election%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20after%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20lost%20its%20special%20status%20in%202019%20and%20was%20bifurcated%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20was%20released%20this%20morning%20after%20the%20BJP's%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20finalised%20the%20party's%20poll%20picks%20for%20the%20upcoming%20election.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20were%20at%20the%20key%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Assembly%20election%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20held%20in%202014.%20In%20the%202014%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20put%20up%20a%20stellar%20show%20by%20winning%2025%20seats%20and%20the%20PDP%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20with%2028%20wins.%20The%20incumbent%20National%20Conference%20won%2015%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20bagged%2012.%20Following%20the%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20PDP%20forged%20a%20surprise%20alliance%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Mufti%20Mohammad%20Sayeed%20and%20then%20by%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20after%20the%20former's%20death%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20headed%20for%20a%20tripartite%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20PDP%20and%20the%20National%20Conference-Congress%20alliance.%20The%20Congress%20and%20National%20Conference%2C%20however%2C%20are%20yet%20to%20iron%20out%20differences%20in%20seat-sharing.%20Top%20Congress%20leaders%20KC%20Venugopal%20and%20Salman%20Khurshid%20have%20been%20rushed%20to%20Srinagar%20to%20clear%20the%20roadblocks%20in%20the%20negotiations%20between%20National%20Conference%20and%20the%20local%20Congress%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20met%20National%20Conference%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20vice-president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20and%20announced%20their%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScoffing%20at%20the%20tie-up%2C%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20Tarun%20Chugh%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20party's%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20campaign%2C%20said%20the%20Congress-National%20Conference%20alliance%20will%20collapse%20like%20a%20house%20of%20cards%20and%20will%20face%20a%20humiliating%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724658120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fu5b487n_bjp-meeting-_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-announces-1st-list-of-candidates-for-jammu-and-kashmir-assembly-polls-6419174%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20today%20released%20a%20list%20of%2044%20candidates%20for%20the%20thr