rs%2C%20from%20the%20stomach%20of%20a%2022-year-old%20man.%20The%20man%20had%20been%20undergoing%20psychiatric%20treatment%20and%20was%20experiencing%20severe%20stomach%20pain.%20After%20a%20surgical%20procedure%2C%20his%20condition%20improved%20and%20he%20will%20soon%20be%20discharged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpatna%2Fdoctors-remove-knife-nail-cutters-key-ring-from-bihar-youths-stomach%2Farticleshow%2F112798845.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPatriarchy%26quot%3B%3A%20Trinamool%20On%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Exit%20Demands%20Over%20Rape-Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20today%20questioned%20demands%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20resignation.%20The%20ruling%20party%20in%20West%20Bengal%20said%20no%20demands%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20exit%20are%20made%20when%20such%20incidents%20take%20place%20in%20other%20states%20and%20claimed%20that%20calls%20for%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20resignation%20are%20an%20expression%20of%20patriarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20so%20many%20incidents%20in%20so%20many%20places.%20Why%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20only%20woman%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20who%20won%20three%20successive%20elections%3F%20No%20demands%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20any%20male%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20incidents%20in%20others%20places.%20That%20is%20how%20patriarchy%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Bengal%20minister%20Chandrima%20Bhattacharya%20told%20the%20media%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Nabanna%20Abhijan%2C%20a%20protest%20march%20announced%20by%20students'%20organisation%20to%20demand%20justice%20for%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%20killed%20in%20the%20chilling%20August%209%20incident.%20The%20march%20to%20the%20state%20secretariat%2C%20due%20tomorrow%2C%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20chaos%20in%20the%20name%20of%20students'%20protest%2C%20Ms%20Bhattacharya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20BJP-ABVP%20plot%20to%20create%20disturbance.%20There%20is%20a%20plot%20to%20open%20fire%20by%20criminals%20in%20police%20uniform.%20Tomorrow%20there%20are%20exams.%20Can%20students%20do%20this%3F%20They%20are%20doing%20vulture%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20permission%20has%20been%20sought%20from%20police%20for%20such%20a%20protest.%20Protests%20can%20take%20place%20but%20they%20have%20to%20take%20permission%20and%20they%20must%20be%20held%20peacefully%20at%20designated%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Kolkata%20and%20neighbouring%20areas%20are%20witnessing%20massive%20protests%20over%20the%20RG%20Kar%20incident%2C%20with%20different%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20hitting%20the%20streets%20daily.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20demanded%20the%20resignation%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20the%20portfolios%20of%20Home%20and%20Health.%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20Opposition%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20and%20Left%20of%20plotting%20unrest%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20led%20a%20rally%20demanding%20justice%20for%20the%20rape-murder%20victim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20everyone%20in%20Trinamool%20wants%20punishment%20for%20the%20guilty%20in%20the%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%2C%20Ms%20Bhattacharya%20questioned%20why%20the%20CBI%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20case%20after%20taking%20over%20the%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20CBI%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20throw%20any%20light%20on%20the%20case%20so%20far.%20Kolkata%20Police%20arrested%20the%20accused%20but%20the%20CBI%20has%20not%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20yet.%20All%20rallies%20demanding%20justice%20should%20culminate%20at%20the%20CGO%20complex%20(where%20CBI%20office%20in%20Kolkata%20is%20located)%20because%20the%20state%20government%20is%20not%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20probe%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrinamool%20Releases%20%26quot%3BNeed%20Bodies%26quot%3B%20Videos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20press%20meet%20this%20morning%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20released%20two%20videos.%20NDTV%20has%20not%20verified%20their%20authenticity.%20In%20the%20videos%2C%20several%20men%20are%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20bodies%26quot%3B.%20Trinamool%20leader%20Jayprakash%20Majumdar%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20create%20unrest%20during%20the%20rally%20to%20Nabanna%20tomorrow.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20leadership%20has%20been%20told%20that%20unless%20a%20Nandigram-type%20incident%20happens%20and%20there%20are%20dead%20bodies%2C%20the%20tide%20will%20not%20turn%20in%20BJP's%20favour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20Trinamool%20leader%20was%20referring%20to%20the%202007%20Nandigram%20violence%20under%20the%20previous%20Left%20government%20in%20Bengal%20which%20claimed%2014%20lives.%C2%A0Mr%20Majumdar%20alleged%20that%20there%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20fire%20at%20protesters%20at%20the%20rally%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Bengal%20Assembly.%20BJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20said%20police%20was%20spreading%20rumours%20to%20disrupt%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMamata%20Police%20is%20deploying%20a%20sinister%20'toolkit'%20to%20redirect%20protesters%20away%20from%20marching%20towards%20Nabanna%2C%20where%20they%20seek%20justice%20for%20the%20RG%20Kar%20PGT%20woman%20doctor.%20The%20West%20Bengal%20Government%20is%20clearly%20shaken%20by%20the%20viral%20call%20for%20the%20'N