ip%20of%2017%25%20last%20quarter.%20Bronfman%20sees%20a%20tech%20collaboration%20as%20vital%20to%20improving%20audience%20growth%2C%20revenue%20generation%2C%20and%20brand%20licensing%2C%20unnamed%20sources%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronfman's%20surprise%20%246%20billion%20bid%20disrupted%20Paramount's%20imminent%20merger%20with%20Skydance%20Media%2C%20which%20was%20set%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20bid%20includes%20buying%20the%20Redstone%20family's%20holding%20company%2C%20National%20Amusements%20Inc.%2C%20which%20controls%20most%20of%20Paramount's%20voting%20stock%2C%20and%20he%20aims%20to%20secure%20more%20shares%20of%20Paramount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bid%20came%20just%20before%20the%2045-day%20%26quot%3Bgo-shop%26quot%3B%20period%20expired%20%E2%80%94%20a%20window%20that%20allowed%20Paramount%20to%20explore%20other%20offers%20even%20after%20announcing%20its%20merger%20with%20Skydance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%20led%20Paramount's%20special%20committee%20to%20extend%20its%20window%20to%20consider%20other%20offers%20by%2015%20days%2C%20CNBC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F08%2F22%2Fparamount-skydance-go-shop-period-extended-to-review-bronfman-offer.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520agreement%2520included%2520a%252045%2Cof%2520a%2520consortium%2520of%2520investors.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkydance%20offered%20to%20inject%20over%20%248%20billion%20into%20Paramount%2C%20but%20Bronfman's%20counteroffer%20includes%20a%20tender%20offer%20giving%20non-voting%20shareholders%20an%20option%20to%20receive%20%2416%20per%20share%2C%20CNBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Bronfman's%20bid%20is%20successful%2C%20he%20would%20take%20over%20as%20CEO%20of%20Paramount%2C%20while%20retaining%20current%20employees.%20Bronfman%20would%20also%20bring%20in%20veteran%20executives%20Jon%20Miller%20and%20John%20Martin%20for%20key%20roles%20in%20the%