2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-jonas-to-meet-the-star-cast-of-paani-visits-film-city-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F112798193.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112798193.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPriyanka%20Chopra%20Jonas%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20attended%20her%20brother%20Siddharth%20Chopra's%20wedding%20festivities.%20Today%2C%20on%20August%2026%2C%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20took%20to%20her%20Instagram%20Stories%20to%20share%20a%20video%20from%20her%20visit%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Film%20City.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-jonas-to-meet-the-star-cast-of-paani-visits-film-city-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F112798193.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mysterious%20Life%20Of%20Telegram%20CEO%20Pavel%20Durov%2C%20Called%20%26quot%3BRussian%20Zuckerberg%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian-born%20tech%20entrepreneur%20Pavel%20Durov%20has%20founded%20wildly%20popular%20social%20networks%20as%20well%20as%20a%20cryptocurrency%2C%20amassed%20a%20multi-billion-dollar%20fortune%20and%20locked%20horns%20with%20authorities%20not%20just%20in%20Russia%20but%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20a%20few%20months%20shy%20of%20his%2040th%20birthday%2C%20the%20man%20once%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BRussian%20Zuckerberg%26quot%3B%20after%20Facebook%20founder%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20now%20finds%20himself%20under%20arrest%20in%20France%20after%20being%20sensationally%20detained%20at%20a%20Paris%20airport%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20still%20in%20his%2020s%2C%20the%20Saint%20Petersburg%20native%20shot%20to%20fame%20in%20Russia%20after%20founding%20the%20VKontakte%20(VK)%20social%20network%20which%20catered%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20Russian-language%20users%20and%20outgunned%20Facebook%20throughout%20the%20former%20USSR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20disputes%20with%20the%20Russian%20authorities%20and%20ownership%20battles%2C%20he%20sold%20out%20of%20VKontakte%20and%20founded%20a%20new%20messaging%20service%20called%20Telegram%20which%20rapidly%20gained%20traction%20but%20has%20also%20proved%20controversial%20with%20critics%20condemning%20an%20alleged%20lack%20of%20control%20on%20extreme%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20dramas%20raged%2C%20Durov%20remained%20a%20mercurial%20and%20at%20times%20mysterious%20figure%2C%20rarely%20giving%20interviews%20and%20restricting%20himself%20to%20sometimes%20enigmatic%20declarations%20made%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20self-avowed%20libertarian%2C%20Durov%20has%20championed%20confidentiality%20on%20the%20Internet%20and%20encryption%20in%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20defiantly%20refused%20to%20allow%20the%20moderation%20of%20messages%20on%20Telegram%2C%20which%20allows%20users%20to%20post%20videos%2C%20pictures%20and%20comments%20on%20%26quot%3Bchannels%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20followed%20by%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurov%2C%2039%2C%20was%20targeted%20in%20France%20by%20a%20warrant%20over%20offences%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20conducted%20on%20Telegram%2C%20ranging%20from%20fraud%20to%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20cyberbullying%20and%20organised%20crime%2C%20including%20promoting%20terrorism%20and%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20have%20been%20entrusted%20to%20the%20cyber%20unit%20of%20the%20French%20gendarmerie%20and%20the%20national%20anti-fraud%20office.%20He%20was%20still%20in%20police%20custody%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20two%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Thanks%20for%20all%20the%20fish'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20having%20just%20graduated%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Saint%20Petersburg%2C%20Durov%20launched%20VKontakte%20(VK)%2C%20attracting%20users%20even%20while%20its%20founder%20remained%20a%20shadowy%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20stunt%20typical%20of%20his%20unpredictable%20behaviour%2C%20Durov%20in%202012%20showered%20high-denomination%20notes%20on%20pedestrians%20from%20VK's%20headquarters%20on%20top%20of%20a%20historic%20bookstore%20on%20Saint%20Petersburg's%20Nevsky%20Prospekt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20running%20into%20trouble%20with%20the%20Kremlin%20for%20refusing%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20users%20to%20the%20Russian%20security%20services%20(FSB)%2C%20he%20sold%20out%20of%20the%20company%20and%20left%20Russia%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurov%20resigned%20from%20VK%20with%20a%20typical%20flourish%2C%20posting%20a%20picture%20of%20dolphins%20and%20the%20slogan%20%26quot%3BSo%20Long%20and%20Thanks%20for%20All%20the%20Fish%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20title%20in%20the%20famous%20%26quot%3BHitchhiker's%20Guide%20to%20the%20Galaxy%26quot%3B%20science%20fiction%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20developed%20the%20Telegram%20messaging%20service%20with%20his%20brother%20Nikolai%20while%20travelling%20from%20country%20to%20country%20and%20launched%20the%20service%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20settled%20in%20Dubai%20and%20obtained%20citizenship%20of%20the%20Caribbean%20island%20archipelago%20of%20Saint%20Kitts%20and%20Nevis%2C%20then%2C%20in%20August%202021%2C%20won%20French%20nationality%20following%20a%20low-profile%20procedure%20about%20which%20Paris%20remains%20highly%20discreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Telegram%20enjoyed%20stratospheric%20success%2C%20presenting%20itself%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20individual%20freedoms%2C%20refusing%20%26quot%3Bcensorship%26quot%3B%20and%20protecting%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20its%20users.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20rankled%20with%20authorities%2C%20especially%20in%20his%20home%20country%20and%20in%202018%2C%20a%20Moscow%20court%20ordered%20the%20blocking%20of%20the%20application.%20But%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20measure%20was%20shambolic%20and%20three%20days%20later%2C%20protesters%20ironically%20bombarded%20the%20FSB%20headquarters%20with%20paper%20planes%2C%20the%20symbol%20of%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Russia%20has%20abandoned%20its%20efforts%20to%20block%20Telegram%20and%20the%20messaging%20service%20is%20used%20by%20both%20the%20Russian%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20with%20some%20channels%20boasting%20several%20hundred%20thousand%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelegram%20also%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20Russia's%20war%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20documented%20by%20bloggers%20from%20both%20sides%20who%20post%20their%20analyses%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20fighting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPro-Moscow%20channels%20run%20by%20so-called%20%26quot%3BZ-bloggers%26quot%3B%20who%20back%20the%20war%20have%20proved%20hugely%20influential%20and%20are%20sometimes%20critical%20of%20Russian%20military%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Love%20the%20privacy'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurov%20eschews%20traditional%20media%20interviews%20but%20in%20April%20sat%20down%20with%20ultra-conservative%20US%20journalist%20Tucker%20Carlson%20for%20an%20extensive%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20%26quot%3Blove%20the%20independence.%20They%20also%20love%20the%20privacy%2C%20the%20freedom%2C%20(there%20are)%20a%20lot%20of%20reasons%20why%20somebody%20would%20switch%20to%20Telegram%2C%26quot%3B%20Durov%20told%20Carlson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20not%20shy%20of%20posting%20messages%20on%20his%20own%20Telegram%20channel%2C%20claiming%20to%20lead%20a%20solitary%20life%2C%20abstaining%20from%20meat%2C%20alcohol%20and%20even%20coffee.%20Always%20dressed%20in%20black%2C%20he%20cultivates%20a%20resemblance%20to%20the%20actor%20Keanu%20Reeves%20in%20the%20film%20%26quot%3BMatrix%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20he%20boasted%20of%20being%20the%20biological%20father%20of%20more%20than%20100%20children%20thanks%20to%20his%20sperm%20donations%20in%20a%20dozen%20countries%2C%20describing%20this%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcivic%20duty%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20attitude%20to%20parenting%20that%20echoes%20that%20of%20a%20fellow%20tech%20mogul%2C%20the%20X%20and%20Tesla%20chief%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Forbes%20magazine's%20latest%20estimate%2C%20Durov's%20fortune%20is%20%2415.5%20billion.%20But%20toncoin%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20he%20created%2C%20has%20plummeted%20by%20more%20than%2015%20per%20cent%20since%20the%20announcement%20of%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelegram%20has%20long%20been%20in%20the%20sights%20of%20European%20judicial%20authorities%20over%20allegations%20it%20spreads%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20shared%20calls%20for%20murder%20and%20hosts%20drug%20sales%20platforms.%20Durov%2C%20however%2C%20insists%20that%20he%20responds%20to%20every%20request%20to%20remove%20content%20calling%20for%20violence%20or%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724654400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2j54hml8_pavel-durov_625x300_25_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmysterious-life-of-telegram-ceo-pavel-durov-called-russian-zuckerberg-6419819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russian-born%20tech%20entrepreneur%20Pavel%20Durov%20has%20founded%20wildly%20popular%20social%20networks%20as%20well%20as%20a%20cryptocurrency%2C%20amassed%20a%20multi-billion-dollar%20fortune%20and%20locked%20horns%20with%20authorities%20not%20just%20in%20Russia%20but%20around%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n