Dispute%20With%20National%20Conference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20clock%20ticking%20on%20finalising%20candidates%20for%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20election%2C%20Congress%20has%20rushed%20troubleshooters%20to%20Srinagar%20to%20clear%20the%20roadblocks%20in%20its%20seat-sharing%20talks%20with%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20date%20for%20filing%20nominations%20for%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20polls%20is%20tomorrow.%20Senior%20Congress%20leaders%20KC%20Venugopal%20and%20Salman%20Khurshid%20will%20be%20meeting%20National%20Conference%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20his%20son%20and%20party%20vice-president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20today%20to%20iron%20out%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20National%20Conference%20has%20offered%20five%20seats%20to%20Congress%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%20and%2028-30%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%20The%20Congress%20is%20demanding%20more%2C%20including%20some%20traditional%20National%20Conference%20strongholds.%20The%20National%20Conference%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20offered%20Congress%20the%20option%20for%20friendly%20contest%20on%20some%20seats%20claimed%20by%20both%2C%20but%20the%20local%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20not%20accepted%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20met%20the%20Abdullahs%20and%20the%20two%20sides%20reached%20on%20agreement%20on%20contesting%20the%20elections%20together.%20But%20differences%20over%20seat-sharing%20emerged%20and%20the%20negotiations%20have%20hit%20a%20roadblock.%20The%20Congress%20has%20now%20rushed%20Mr%20Venugopal%20and%20Mr%20Khurshid%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20impasse%20so%20that%20the%20parties%20can%20focus%20on%20prepping%20for%20the%20key%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENinety%20seats%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20are%20voting%20in%20three%20phases%2C%20with%20polling%20due%20on%20September%2018%2C%20September%2025%20and%20October%201.%20Counting%20of%20votes%20is%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20were%20last%20held%20in%202014%20after%20which%20the%20PDP%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Centre%20revoked%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20bifurcated%20the%20state%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20last%20week%20said%20seat-sharing%20with%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20finalised%20for%20most%20assembly%20seats%20and%20talks%20are%20on%20to%20reach%20consensus%20over%20the%20ones%20remaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsensus%20has%20been%20reached%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20we%20have%20reached%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20maximum%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2090%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20few%20seats%2C%20we%20are%20adamant%20and%20on%20some%20others%2C%20the%20local%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20are%20adamant.%20There%20will%20be%20meetings%20today%20as%20well%20and%20we%20will%20try%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20seats%20so%20as%20to%20announce%20our%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20hit%20out%20sharply%20at%20the%20Congress's%20decision%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20National%20Conference%20for%20the%20key%20election.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20risking%20the%20%26quot%3Bnation's%20unity%20and%20security%20to%20satiate%20its%20greed%20for%20power%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Shah%20questioned%20if%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20support%20National%20Conference's%20promises%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20separate%20flag%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Brestoration%20of%20Article%20370%20and%2035A%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20asked%20if%20the%20Congress