0in%20a%20relaxed%20pose%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20chair%2C%20holding%20a%20cigarette%20and%20a%20coffee%20cup%2C%20while%20in%20the%20company%20of%20three%20other%20individuals.%20According%20to%20some%20reports%2C%20those%20seen%20with%20Darshan%20include%20criminal%20Wilson%20Garden%20Naga%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Nagaraj%2C%20the%20actor's%20manager%20and%20co-accused%2C%20and%20Kulla%20Seena%2C%20another%20inmate.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20video%20allegedly%20showing%20Darshan%20speaking%20to%20someone%20over%20a%20video%20call%20has%20also%20been%20circulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20triggered%20widespread%20criticism%2C%20with%20many%20expressing%20outrage%20over%20the%20preferential%20treatment%20allegedly%20given%20to%20Darshan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%2C%20along%20with%2016%20others%2C%20including%20his%20friend%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20is%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20Renukaswamy.%20The%20case%20has%20drawn%20significant%20attention%20due%20to%20Darshan's%20celebrity%20status%20and%20the%20brutal%20nature%20of%20the%20crime.%20According%20to%20police%20sources%2C%2033-year-old%20Renukaswamy%2C%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20actor%2C%20had%20allegedly%20sent%20obscene%20messages%20to%20Ms%20Gowda%2C%20which%20reportedly%20provoked%20Darshan%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20the%20fan's%20murder.%20The%20victim's%20body%20was%20discovered%20near%20a%20stormwater%20drain%20next%20to%20an%20apartment%20on%20June%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashinath%20S%20Shivanagowdru%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Renukaswamy%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20and%20the%20punishment%20of%20those%20responsible.%20%26quot%3BWith%20such%20things%2C%20there%20is%20a%20feeling%20that%20a%20CBI%20probe%20should%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20picture%2C%20I'm%20surprised%20to%20see%20him%20(Darshan)%20with%20others%20holding%20a%20cigarette%20and%20dr