h%2C%20the%2084-year-old%20Nobel%20laureate%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20maintain%20friendly%20relations%20with%20all%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.Mutual%20trust%20and%20cooperation%20will%20be%20the%20base%20of%20our%20foreign%20policy.%20We%20are%20respectful%20of%20all%20international%20laws%2C%20including%20human%20rights.%20We%20have%20taken%20steps%20to%20become%20signatory%20to%20the%20international%20convention%20on%20enforced%20disappearances%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20official%20BSS%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20said%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20election%20is%20a%20political%20decision%20and%20people%20will%20decide%20how%20long%20this%20interim%20government%20will%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20assured%20the%20nation%20that%20his%20interim%20government%20will%20hold%20free%2C%20fair%20and%20inclusive%20elections%20in%20the%20country%20after%20undertaking%20reforms%20in%20various%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20completion%20of%20required%20reforms%20in%20administration%2C%20judiciary%2C%20election%20commission%20and%20electoral%20system%2C%20law%20and%20order%20and%20information%20flow%20systems%20--%20a%20free%2C%20fair%20and%20inclusive%20election%20will%20be%20held%20to%20give%20the%20student-people%20mass%20protests%20a%20successful%20consequence%2C%26quot%3B%20Yunus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20committee%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20already%20been%20formed%20to%20prepare%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20corruption%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20anti-people%20agreements%20and%20looting%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20last%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%2C%20who%20now%20serves%20as%20the%20Chief%20Adviser%20-%20a%20position%20equivalent%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20said%20his%20interim%20government%20would%20strengthen%20the%20local%20government%20institutions%20and%20ensure%20decentralisation%20to%20consolidate%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20will%20be%20to%20introduce%20an%20accountable%20political%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yunus%2C%20who%20assumed%20charge%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Hasina%20amid%20a%20massive%20students'%20movement%20that%20also%20forced%20her%20to%20flee%20to%20India.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20Yunus%20did%20not%20give%20any%20deadline%20for%20the%20tenure%20of%20his%20interim%20government%20but%20acknowledged%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceveryone%20is%20interested%20to%20know%20when%20our%20government%20will%20leave%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20answer%20lies%20with%20you%20when%20you%20will%20give%20us%20the%20farewell.%20None%20of%20us%20(council%20of%20advisers)%20are%20the%20ones%20to%20rule%20the%20country.%20We%20are%20happy%20with%20our%20professions.%20We%20took%20charge%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20students'%20call%20during%20a%20national%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20said%20that%20his%20government%20would%20%E2%80%9Cput%20in%20all%20our%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20to%20discharge%20the%20duty%20he%20has%20been%20entrusted%20with%20as%20all%20sections%20of%20people%20had%20welcomed%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20adviser%20slammed%20Hasina's%20%26quot%3Bfascist%20autocratic%20regime%E2%80%9D%2C%20saying%20they%20destroyed%20every%20institution%20of%20the%20country%2C%20crippled%20the%20economy%20and%20education%20system%2C%20and%20gauged%20people's%20voices%20through%20intimidation%20and%20torture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20said%20his%20government%20believed%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20unity%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20that%20reason%2C%20he%20has%20appointed%20a%20special%20assistant%20with%20the%20status%20of%20an%20adviser%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20developing%20national%20solidarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20said%20the%20main%20aim%20of%20the%20election%20is%20to%20introduce%20an%20accountable%20political%20system%20against%20corruption%2C%20looting%20and%20