said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20declare%20the%20first%20innings%20on%20448%20for%20six%20was%20taken%20to%20push%20for%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20go%20for%20a%20win%20in%20the%20match%20and%20thus%20felt%20we%20had%20enough%20runs%20on%20the%20board%20to%20declare.%20But%20the%20Bangladesh%20batters%20showed%20a%20lot%20of%20discipline%20and%20intent%20in%20their%20first%20innings.%20Mushfiq%20and%20Miraz%20batted%20really%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20felt%20that%20with%20448%20runs%20we%20could%20get%20a%20crack%20at%20them%20in%20the%20fourth%20innings.%E2%80%9D%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20have%20done%20with%20more%20runs%20but%20there%20were%20also%20things%20with%20the%20ball%20and%20in%20the%20field%20that%20we%20could've%20done%20better%20to%20either%20take%20a%20lead%20or%20keep%20them%20at%20par%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20just%2030%20runs%2C%20openers%20Zakir%20Hasan%20and%20Shadman%20Islam%20guided%20Bangladesh%20to%20the%20target%20in%206.3%20overs%20without%20losing%20a%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20starting%20the%20day%20at%2065%20for%202%2C%20crumbled%20against%20Bangladesh's%20spinners%2C%20losing%20their%20last%20eight%20wickets%20for%20just%2081%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20skipper%20conceded%20it%20was%20not%20the%20ideal%20start%20to%20the%20home%20season%20where%20the%20team%20had%20to%20play%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20Tests%20at%20home%20and%20two%20away%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20have%20to%20now%20get%20everything%20right%20and%20try%20to%20level%20the%20series%20in%20the%20world%20test%20championship%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunday's%20defeat%20was%20Shan's%20fourth%20straight%20defeat%20as%20captain%20after%20Pakistan's%200-3%20whitewash%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Australia%20last%20winter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this