ause%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20and%20seeing%20dirty%20edited%20content%20of%20me%20as%20a%20child%3F%20No.%20It's%20terrifying.%20It's%20corrupt.%20It's%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20child%20actor%2C%20who%20rose%20to%20fame%20starring%20in%20the%20Disney%20Channel%20series%20%26quot%3BStuck%20in%20the%20Middle%26quot%3B%20and%20CW%20comedy%20%26quot%3BJane%20the%20Virgin%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20she%20was%20told%20to%20sign%20up%20to%20Twitter%20to%20build%20her%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenna%20Ortega%20in%20Stuck%20in%20the%20middle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65141a0c1c099d0019ad2c0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenna%20Ortega%20rose%20to%20fame%20as%20a%20child%20star%20on%20Disney%20Channel's%20%26quot%3BStuck%20in%20the%20Middle.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EEric%20McCandless%20%2F%20Disney%20Channel%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20first%20%E2%80%94%20actually%20the%20first%20D.M.%20that%20I%20ever%20opened%20myself%20when%20I%20was%2012%20was%20an%20unsolicited%20photo%20of%20a%20man's%20genitals%2C%20and%20that%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20what%20was%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20said%20that%20she%20ended%20up%20deleting%20the%20app%20%26quot%3Babout%20two%2C%20three%20years%20ago%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Binflux%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20images%20and%20photos%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20receiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20disgusting%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20bad.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20uncomfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnyway%2C%20that's%20why%20I%20deleted%20it%2C%20because%20I%20couldn't%20say%20anything%20without%20seeing%20something%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20isn't%20the%20first%20person%20to%2