0have%20no%20smell.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20sugar%20has%20been%20tampered%20with%20urea%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20a%20pungent%20ammonia-like%20odour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20HCL%20Test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJaggery%2C%20a%20natural%20sweetener%2C%20is%20another%20product%20that%20can%20be%20adulterated.%20To%20test%20for%20this%2C%20take%20some%20crushed%20jaggery%20and%20place%20it%20in%20a%20test%20tube.%20Add%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20Hydrochloric%20acid%20(HCL)%20to%20it.%20If%20the%20jaggery%20starts%20bubbling%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20sign%20that%20it%20has%20been%20mixed%20with%20impurities%20like%20baking%20soda%20or%20washing%20powder.%20Pure%20jaggery%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20will%20not%20react%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rising%20cases%20of%20food%20adulteration%20and%20growing%20concerns%20over%20food%20safety%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20to%20be%20vigilant.%20Taking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352550%2Fhow-to-check-spices-purity-at-home-adulteration-indian-red-chili-powder-hing-turmeric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20a%20few%20minutes%20to%20perform%20these%20simple%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20you%20ensure%20that%20the%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20jaggery%20in%20your%20kitchen%20are%20pure%2C%20safeguarding%20your%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftoxicslink.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPress%2520Release_English_Microplastics%2520In%2520Salt%2520and%2520Sugar_Toxics%2520Link%2520Study.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEating%20Lots%20Of%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20%26amp%3B