0nowadays.%20We%20are%20successful%20in%20stopping%20many%20of%20these.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlowing%20the%20whistle%20on%20a%20practice%20that%20has%20been%20customary%20for%20years%20now%2C%20must%20be%20tough%2C%20I%20assume.%20Kamble%20mirrors%20the%20sentiment.%20But%20he%20insists%20that%20in%20every%20undertaking%20of%20good%20work%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20some%20resistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20an%20anecdote%20of%20his%20college%20days%2C%20when%20he%20was%20pursuing%20his%20MSW%20(Masters%20in%20Social%20Work)%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20very%20little%20awareness%20about%20blood%20donation%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20started%20working%20with%20a%20few%20friends%20to%20organise%20camps%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20donate%20blood.%20But%20the%20donors%E2%80%99%20parents%20weren%E2%80%99t%20too%20happy%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20berate%20him%20for%20forcing%20their%20wards%20into%20giving%20blood%20which%20they%20believed%20would%20%E2%80%9Cmake%20them%20less%20human%E2%80%9D.%20But%20gradually%2C%20the%20notion%20was%20dispelled%20and%20Kamble%20became%20the%20first%20point%20of%20contact%20in%20cases%20where%20someone%20needed%20blood%20for%20a%20relative%20or%20friend.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208322%2Fbengaluru-teen-teacher-death-blood-donation-community-inspiring-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20donation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20connected%20him%20with%20doctors%2C%20paramedics%2C%20social%20workers%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20network%20that%20he%20now%20relies%20on%20for%20information%20on%20child%20marriages%20in%20Beed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kamble%20interjects%2C%20technology%20has%20proved%20very%20resourceful%2C%20especially%20WhatsApp.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20send%20the