%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Somnath%20started%20%E2%80%98Dihadi%20Kitchen%E2%80%99%20in%20Lucknow%20to%20provide%20regular%2C%20hygienic%20meals%20to%20labourers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESomnath%20started%20%E2%80%98Dihadi%20Kitchen%E2%80%99%20in%20Lucknow%20to%20provide%20regular%2C%20hygienic%20meals%20to%20labourers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20swiftly%20grew%20into%20a%20structured%20offering%2C%20turning%20into%20a%20community-supported%20endeavour%20that%20today%20feeds%20about%203%2C000%20labourers%20every%20week%20with%20meals%20like%20%3Cem%3Epuri%20sabji%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20nutritious%20lentils%20with%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20seek%20help%20through%20crowdfunding%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomnath%E2%80%99s%20mission%20is%20supported%20significantly%20through%20social%20media%2C%20which%20allows%20him%20to%20connect%20with%20and%20inspire%20a%20broader%20audience.%20The%20model%20he%20adopted%20demonstrates%20his%20belief%20in%20the%20collective%20power%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20he%20incurs%20costs%20of%20roughl