%20achieve%20the%20necessary%20speed%20for%20a%20100-metre%20lap%20during%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20was%20holding%20her%20back%20%E2%80%94%20her%20father%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20given%20her%20his%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiran%20Chavan%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20his%20daughter%20wanted%20to%20put%20herself%20through%20such%20a%20demanding%20ordeal.%20He%20was%20apprehensive%2C%20knowing%20of%20people%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20attempting%20this%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20her%20to%20put%20herself%20in%20a%20life-threatening%20position.%20She%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20her%20business%2C%20as%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Why%20put%20your%20life%20at%20risk%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20protect%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tanvi%20was%20determined%20and%20persuasive.%20When%20letters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20she%20asked%20her%20coach%20to%20convince%20her%20father.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20her%20coach%20met%20me%20and%20assured%20me%20that%20there%20was%20no%20risk%20of%20life%20and%20she%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20it%20convinced%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMagically%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20required%20timing%20the%20next%20day%20and%20since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20She%20slowly%20gained%20her%20confidence%20back%20and%20started%20practice%20in%20earnest%20for%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20big%20challenge%20to%20tackle%20was%20the%20cold%20conditions%20of%20the%20English%20Channel.%20To%20get%20acclimatised%20to%20cold%20water%2C%20Tanvi%20first%20started%20taking%20only%20cold%20showers.%20She%20also%20started%20sitting%20in%20ice%20baths%20for%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20later%20increased%20to%20one%20hour.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20sit%20in%20ice%20water%20from%202%20am%20to%203%20am%20to%20get%20used%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361699%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20practised%20in%20Nainital%E2%80%99s%20Naini%20lake%20for%20a%20week%2C%20which%20has%20conditions%20similar%20to%20the%20English%20Channel.%20Unfortunately%2C%20when%20she%20reached%20Nainital%2C%20it%20snowed%2C%20which%20made%20the%20water%20extremely%20cold.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20coach%20motivated%20me%20to%20swim.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20it%E2%80%99.%20I%20swam%20in%2011%20degrees%20Celsius%20water%20temperature%2C%20which%20helped%20my%20body%20get%20used%20to%20such%20cold%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaging%20time%20became%20a%20significant%20challenge%20for%20Tanvi.%20She%20would%20practice%20in%20the%20morning%20from%204%20am%20to%207%20am%2C%20send%20the%20kids%20off%20to%20school%2C%20go%20to%20the%20office%2C%20and%20then%20practice%20again%20in%20the%20evening%20before%20finally%20heading%20to%20bed.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20each%20day%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20utterly%20exhausted.%20The%20physical%20pain%20and%20lack%20of%20proper%20sleep%20began%20to%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20her%2C%20hindering%20her%20recovery%20and%20adding%20to%20the%20overall%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20more%20time%20for%20herself%2C%20she%20completely%20cut%20off%20from%20social%20media%20and%20social%20engagements%20during%20the%20last%20seven%20months%20of%20training.%20This%20simple%20change%20saved%20her%20almost%20four%20hours%20every%20day%20and%20she%20slept%20at%208%3A30%20pm%20with%20her%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPractice%20intensified%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20Tanvi%20took%20a%20break%20from%20work%20two%20months%20before%20the%20challenge%20and%20focused%20only%20on%20practice.%20She%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208604%2Findia-record-para-swimmer-satendra-singh-lohia-first-asian-catalina-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswim%20for%20eight%20hours%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eat%20well%2C%20rest%20and%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20month%20before%20the%20actual%20attempt%2C%20Tanvi%20and%20her%20family%20went%20to%20Dover%2C%20UK%20to%20practise%20on%20the%20beach.%20Swimming%20in%20the%20exact%20same%20conditions%20helped%20the%20swimmer%E2%80%99s%20body%20get%20used%20to%20the%20cold%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Never%20thought%20of%20giving%20up%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED-day%3A%2029%20June%2C%202024%2C%203%3A30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20started%20the%20%E2%80%98Mount%20Everest%20of%20Swimming%E2%80%99%20from%20Dover.%20In%20a%20boat%20following%20her%20were%20two%20pilots%2C%20an%20observer%20from%20the%20Channel%20Swimming%20Association%2C%20her%20coach%2C%20husband%2C%20and%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20father%20who%20was%20unwilling%20to%20let%20his%20daughter%20take%20such%20a%20big%20risk%20was%20now%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader.%20At%2064%2C%20he%20had%20to%20wage%20a%20battle%20to%20be%20allowed%20on%20the%20boat.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20usually%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20people%20above%2060%20on%20the%20boat%20as%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20sea%20sickness.%20I%20had%20to%20be%20there%20for%20Tanvi%20and%20had%20only%20juices%20for%20two%20days%20before%20and%20carried%20medicines%20to%20prevent%20vomiting%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9zlIvVu6_M%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9zlIvVu6_M%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9zlIvVu6_M%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%40swimwithtanvi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20started%20her%20swim%20on%20a%20high%20note%2C%20alongside%20seven%20other%20swimmers%20who%20were%20also%20attempting%20to%20conquer%20the%20English%20Channel.%20However%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20she%20faced%20during%20her%20swim%20was%20jellyfish.%20Hundreds%20of%20them%20stung%20her%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20already%20immense%20difficulty%20of%20the%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20very%20painful%3B%20I%20almost%20felt%20a%20shock%2C%20an%20electric%20current%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20my%20body%20to%20move%20for%20almost%2020%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20swimming%20for%20nearly%2011%20to%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20weather%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20with%20high%20tides%20and%20strong%20currents%20making%20progress%20nearly%20impossible.%20Despite%20her%20continuous%20efforts%2C%20Tanvi%20found%20herself%20stuck%20in%20place.%20The%20observer%20on%20her%20support%20boat%20cautioned%20that%20crossing%20the%20channel%20would%20be%20difficult%20under%20such%20conditions.%20This%20treacherous%20region%20of%20the%20English%20Channel%20is%20notoriously%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98swimmer%E2%80%99s%20grave%E2%80%99%20due%20to%20its%20unforgiving%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20three%20hours%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20trapped%20in%20these%20relentless%20currents%2C%20her%20resilience%20tested%20to%20the%20limit.%20The%20situation%20grew%20even%20more%20daunting%20as%20three%20of%20her%20fellow%20swimmers%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20attempts%20due%20to%20the%20worsening%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20waves%20were%20two%20to%20three%20metres%20in%20height%20and%20pulled%20you%20back%20to%20England.%20I%20was%20trapped%20in%20this%20and%20had%20to%20swim%20an%20extra%2010%20kilometres%20to%20reach%20the%20French%20coast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tanvi%20pressed%20on%20and%20covered%20the%20additional%2010%20kilometres%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20weather.%20When%20the%20observer%20asked%20if%20she%20wished%20to%20continue%2C%20it%20was%20an%20emphatic%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20actually%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20I%20had%20vomited%20and%20had%20zero%20energy.%20It%20was%20thanks%20to%20my%20coach%E2%80%99s%20training%20that%20I%20was%20mentally%20fit%20to%20continue.%20He%20had%20told%20me%20that%20it%20is%20on%20days%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20training%20are%20the%20days%20that%20you%20must%20show%20up.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20your%20hands%20and%20legs%20reach%20their%20breaking%20point%2C%20you%20will%20feel%20like%20giving%20up.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20up!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20her%20morale%2C%20her%20husband%20showed%20her%20a%20video%20of%20their%20children%20and%20the%20coach%20showed%20her%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20swim%20for%20my%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%